creator: Mischief Cat, LLC
descriptionHtml:
Discover a brand new world with Detective Evi Dents. Challenge your brain with these code-breaking logic puzzles.

STORY MODE
Join Detective Evi on a comical mystery as she investigates the whereabouts of famed engineer Hugh M. Aye. Guided by the professor's son, Yuu, the duo soon get caught up in a mystery deeper than they thought involving a mysterious phantom bent on stopping their progress.

Help Evi and Yuu unravel mysteries and dig up clues while solving fun code-breaking puzzles that progressively increase in difficulty. Will Evi and Yuu ever be able to find the missing Professor?

Full of a quirky cast of characters, Story Mode is a charming way to challenge yourself with puzzles.

QUICK PLAY
Looking for puzzles? Now they're just a quick tap away. Customize the difficulty of your puzzles and add time and move limits to give you an extra challenge!

PROFESSOR'S CHALLENGE
Each day offers you a fun new challenge.

OTHER FEATURES
- Polished, high quality art with a distinctive style
- Achievement challenges for players to unlock
- Track your progress through the statistics menu

PRIVACY POLICY & TERMS OF SERVICE
